    hprior_pos hsubA_pos hsubB_pos htestA_pos htestB_pos

/--
Paper Theorem 2(i): if the CDF/threshold derivation identifies diversity
improvement with Equation (4), then diversity improves exactly when the
paper's Equation (3) test-precision ratio holds.
