/--
Proposition 5(i) / Theorem 3(i) positive-interval objective bridge with the
paper's capacity-fill contradiction.  The conclusion keeps the condition-(10)
threshold on `[leftCost_g,rightCost_g]` and uses the paper-level `K` notation.
