    hshareA hshareB hmassFullFullA hmassFullFullB hcapacity1
    hfillFullFull1 hnoneJ1 honlyA_J1_merit honlyB_J1_merit
    hJ2ObjectiveSubSub hJ2ObjectiveSubFullB hJ2MassB hJ2NotTieB
    hJ2ObjectiveSubFullA hJ2MassA hJ2NotTieA

